{"tid":1474956,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰你今次仲唔死？","createTime":"2019-08-15T10:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:03:58.000Z","uid":267018,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5188575e8e319118fe9880089d19e32a9d9426","tid":1474956,"uid":267018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/209641255886389/posts/1160786124105226?s=1122507307&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F209641255886389%2Fposts%2F1160786124105226%3Fs%3D1122507307%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdmSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=fe242408\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/209641255886389/posts/1160786124105226?s=1122507307&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲有冇睇過呢個post?<br />\n雖然國泰呢幾年變咗因航，但似乎佢係制行大陸航空業方面有好重要嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果連我地都罷買國泰，就變撚哂豬隊友，國航就笑到gap gap 聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我好憂心，心疲到訓着咗<br />\n<br />\n夢見而家AA申請咗禁制令，淨係准有飛嘅旅客入機場大堂<br />\n跟住我見到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多手足買咗張最平嘅國泰機票</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連飛機餐都冇訂<br />\n入咗去，唔小心蕩失路/掛住參觀機場/排隊疴屎...搞到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">miss咗班機</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住佢地好緊張，要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留係機場等補飛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住 我就醒咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d84fdefd32caac8024ad52b608da10ef4781fd","tid":1474956,"uid":111316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"米撚佢啦 佢會仆街有一半係支持個運動<br />\n明明仲有咁撚多大陸航空<br />\n要玩都玩其他先"},{"pid":"1033f6f6ee